<template>
    <v-carousel class="carousel"
        cycle
        height="400"
        hide-delimiter-background
        show-arrows-on-hover>
        <v-carousel-item
            v-for="image in images"
            :key="image.id">
            <v-sheet
                :color="colors[i]"
                height="100%">
                <v-row
                    class="fill-height"
                    align="center"
                    justify="center">
                    <v-img :src="image.src" />
                </v-row>
            </v-sheet>
        </v-carousel-item>
    </v-carousel>
</template>
<script>
    import { images } from '@core/shared/mockdata/images.js';

    export default {
        data () {
            return {
                images: images,
                colors: [
                    'indigo',
                    'warning',
                    'pink darken-2',
                    'red lighten-1',
                    'deep-purple accent-4',
                ],
                slides: [
                    'First',
                    'Second',
                    'Third',
                    'Fourth',
                    'Fifth',
                ],
            };
        },
    };
</script>

<style scoped>
    .carousel {
        width: 80%;
        margin: auto;
    }

    .button {
        background: white;
    }
</style>
